            <description><![CDATA[<div class="figure-media"><img class="img-fluid lazyload" data-src="/s3fs-public/styles/article_large_full/public/2022-12/laiqingde.jpg?itok=5zV9nZNY" title="台湾副总统赖清德决定参选民进党主席。（自由时报）" alt="台湾副总统赖清德决定参选民进党主席。（自由时报）" src="https://www.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/styles/article_large_full/public/2022-12/laiqingde.jpg?itok=5zV9nZNY" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div>
